	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000937_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">Tuesday Morning</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Doctor Loudon</p>
<lb/><p>Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p>Will you 
<lb/>favour me with a 
<lb/>call as soon as 
<lb/>may be convenient 
<lb/>to you. I have 
<lb/>a bad cold and 
<lb/>as it is expected 
<lb/>that I employ 
<lb/>my voice soon 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000937_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>I wish if possible 
<lb/>to get rid of the 
<lb/>hoarseness. If 
<lb/>you think a 
<lb/>mustard plaister 
<lb/>advisable please 
<lb/>bring it with 
<lb/>you. I should 
<lb/>like an aperient 
<lb/>and the resin of 
<lb/>Jalap with calomel 
<lb/>suits me better 
<lb/>in the form of 
<lb/>pill. than some 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000937_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/><!-- hand 01 top right 766-->others in liquid form 
<lb/>but I shall take 
<lb/>anything you may 
<lb/>consider better</p>
<lb/><p>Pray excuse my 
<lb/>apparent dictation 
<lb/>&amp; oblige yours 
<lb/>Most Truly</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingston</p>
<lb/><p><unclear cert="medium">Burnbank Road</unclear></p>
			
</div>
